# Data

The AMI Meeting Corpus is not included in this repository.
It can be obtained from:
- Public release: http://corpus.amiproject.org/
- Or by contacting the original authors directly.

Place the corpus in this directory with the following structure:
data/
└── ami_corpus/
    ├── words/          (word-level transcript XML files)
    ├── dialogueActs/   (NXT-format dialogue act XML files)
    ├── meetings.xml
    └── participants.xml

The analysis uses the 120 scenario meetings (ES, IS, TS groups)
with complete word-level transcripts and dialogue act annotations.
